forts.","id":"b3bcb008-cf1f-4849-8450-f5f220fc1888","is_major":false,"source":"Business Wire","source_type":"news","summary":"In Dallas, a prominent provider of employee scheduling and attendance solutions, TCP Software, has recently bolstered its executive leadership team in the last six months. Stu Story has been named the Chief Revenue Officer, Casey Carey is now the Chief Marketing Officer, and Praveen Kanyadi was appointed as the SVP of Product Management. These key additions are geared towards propelling TCP's growth trajectory by strengthening its emphasis on customer satisfaction and introducing cutting-edge solutions in the workplace.","tickers":["BKX"],"time":"20:24:27","timestamp":"2024-10-24T20:24:27Z","url":"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20241024216756/en/TCP-Software-Welcomes-New-Executives-as-the-Company-Focuses-on-Increasing-Customer-Value-and-Product-Innovation/?feedref=JjAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-Q-tiwWZwkcswR1UZtV7eGe24xL9TZOyQUMS3J72mJlQ7fxFuNFTHSunhvli30RlBNXya2izy9YOgHlBiZQk2LOzmn6JePCpHPCiYGaEx4DL1Rq8pNwkf3AarimpDzQGuQ=="},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"securities","date":"2024-10-24","headline":"DryEye Rescue expands into broader eye care market with Vision Rescue launch in 2024. #EyeCare #Expansion #VisionRescue","id":"e3a7d17a-90c9-4c3d-a022-72b29833f7ce","is_major":false,"source":"PR NewsWire","source_type":"news","summary":"Vision Rescue has announced the expansion of its product offerings to include comprehensive solutions for eye care facilities, moving beyond dry eye care. The announcement was made in Boca Raton, Florida on October 24, 2024. DryEye Rescue, a prominent marketing solutions provider for eye care providers, is spearheading this initiative. This expansion aims to cater to a wider range of eye care needs and enhance the company's market presence.","tickers":["BKX"],"time":"20:24:23","timestamp":"2024-10-24T20:24:23Z","url":"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/dryeye-rescue-launches-vision-rescue-to-serve-a-broader-eye-care-market-302286581.html"},{"beta_headline":null,"category":"securities","date":"2024-10-24","headline":"Yoga Joint in Boca Raton, Florida raised $12 million for expansion through crowdfunding from members.","id":"b05b1050-48db-43d3-8714-bf853fde3a52","is_major":false,"source":"PR NewsWire","source_type":"news","summary":"In Boca Raton, Florida on October 24, 2024, Yoga Joint, a leading chain of hot yoga and fitness studios in South Florida, revealed that its Joint Venture Program has triumphantly secured $12 million in funding through crowdfunding from its loyal community of members. This significant sum of $12 million...","tickers":["BKX"],"time":"20:24:21","timestamp":"2024-10-24T20:24:21Z","url":"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/yoga-joint-raises-12-million-to-continue-florida-expansion-302286590.html"}]}